From 0 to 24 on March 5,31 provinces (autonomous regions and municipalities directly under the Central Government) and Xinjiang Production and Construction Corps reported 143 new confirmed cases, 30 new deaths (29 in Hubei and 1 in Hainan) , and 102 new suspected cases.

On the same day, 1681 cases were cured, 5457 close contacts were removed from medical observation, and 215 cases of severe cases were reduced.

As of 2400 hours on March 5,31 provinces (autonomous regions and municipalities directly under the Central Government) and Xinjiang Production and Construction Corps have reported 23,784 confirmed cases (including 5,737 severe cases) , 53,726 discharged cases and 3,042 deaths, a total of 80552 confirmed cases and 482 suspected cases have been reported. A total of 670854 close contacts were traced and 29,896 close contacts remained under medical observation.
